SpatiumDDI Appliance — Bundled Open-Source Components

This appliance image bundles software from the projects listed below.
SpatiumDDI itself is licensed under the Apache License 2.0 (see
/usr/share/doc/spatiumddi/LICENSE in the SpatiumDDI containers, or
https://github.com/spatiumddi/spatiumddi/blob/main/LICENSE).

The full text of each license is available on the system at
/usr/share/doc/<package>/copyright. Source for each component is
available via Debian's source tree:

   apt-get source <package>

or upstream:

   https://sources.debian.org/

